# Yangi Bozor Residence - Real Estate Landing Page

## Project Structure
- Root directory: Contains index.html and supporting config files
- /static/: Main directory for all assets
  - /static/css/: CSS files organized in modular structure
    - /base/: Base styles and resets
    - /components/: Reusable component styles
    - /sections/: Page section-specific styles
  - /static/js/: JavaScript files
    - /components/: Modular JS components
    - main.js: Core functionality
    - config.js: Configuration parameters
    - enhancements.js: Additional features
  - /static/images/: Image assets

## Technologies
- HTML5 semantic markup
- CSS3 with modular organization
- Vanilla JavaScript (no frameworks)
- Font Awesome 6.0.0 for icons
- Google Fonts (Open Sans, Playfair Display)
- Chart.js for data visualization

## Components
1. Hero Slider
   - Auto rotation (8-second intervals)
   - Pause on hover functionality
   - Touch swipe support
   - Parallax effects on desktop
   - Dot navigation

2. Navigation
   - Sticky header with scroll effects
   - Mobile hamburger menu
   - Smooth scrolling to sections

3. Floor Plans Interface
   - Interactive apartment selection
   - Dynamic display of apartment details
   - Plan image switching

4. Project Galleries
   - Modal sliders for projects
   - Next/previous controls
   - Keyboard navigation

5. Weather Integration
   - OpenWeather API
   - Location configuration in config.js
   - Historical data visualization

6. Interactive Features
   - Back to top button
   - Language toggle (RU/EN)
   - Interactive map with points of interest
   - Floating contact button
   - Infinite carousel for amenities

## Accessibility Features
- Skip to content link
- ARIA labels
- Keyboard navigation support
- Screen reader considerations
- Alt text for images

## Responsive Design
- Mobile-first approach
- Breakpoints for various screen sizes
- Touch-friendly interactions on mobile
- Optimized images and content display

## Third-Party Services
- OpenWeather API for weather data
- Font Awesome for iconography
- Google Fonts for typography

## Performance Considerations
- Debounced event handlers
- Throttled scroll listeners
- Image optimization
- Animation performance tuning